    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>couscous</strong> and <strong>diced apricots</strong> to a large dish or bowl with 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cover and set aside</p><p>Add the<strong> courgette ribbons</strong> to a pot or separate heat-proof bowl and cover with hot water for 4 min, then drain and squeeze out any excess water with your hands</p>",
      "order": 2,
