    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
